WEBVTT

00:07.542 --> 00:10.411
Give me them jewels, Finn.
We're out of time.

00:10.445 --> 00:12.313
[ Cackles ]

00:12.347 --> 00:15.015
Now, let's grab LSP and get
the buns out of here.

00:15.049 --> 00:17.318
Huh!

00:17.352 --> 00:20.087
[ Laughs ]

00:22.189 --> 00:25.260
♪ Let me hear you whisper

00:25.293 --> 00:26.861
Aah!

00:26.894 --> 00:28.896
You left my friend Finn
down there.

00:28.929 --> 00:30.898
I'm sorry, but we don't need
him anymore.

00:30.931 --> 00:33.000
But don't worry,
I've got a new plan.

00:33.033 --> 00:35.370
A plan where nothing that
happens here matters.

00:35.403 --> 00:38.773
Okay, but we should
turn back still.

00:38.806 --> 00:40.408
Finn loves me.

00:40.441 --> 00:43.244
He sees me as, like,
a handsome older brother.

00:45.480 --> 00:47.382
Mm, no.
I'm doing the right thing.

00:47.415 --> 00:49.550
Can't go around it,
got to go through it.

00:49.584 --> 00:53.120
♪ That you love me, too

00:53.153 --> 00:55.523
Uh, guys?
Getting a little too close.

00:55.556 --> 00:57.925
♪ Keep the love-light glowing
Uh... uh.

00:57.958 --> 01:01.429
♪ In your eyes so true

01:01.462 --> 01:04.198
♪ Let me call you sweetheart
[ Screams ]

01:04.231 --> 01:07.034
Finn, it's me,
I'm saving your tight butt!

01:07.067 --> 01:10.738
[ Grunts ]
Whoop!

01:10.771 --> 01:12.807
Don't worry, my children.

01:12.840 --> 01:16.877
I will send my joy out
unto all of them.

01:16.911 --> 01:19.914
"Bonbon ballad."

01:19.947 --> 01:22.550
♪ Underneath the mountain

01:22.583 --> 01:24.785
♪ Overlook the sea

01:24.819 --> 01:26.987
♪ I find my sweet friends
waiting ♪

01:27.021 --> 01:30.090
♪ And bring them close to me

01:30.124 --> 01:34.762
♪ La-da-da-da, la-da-da

01:34.795 --> 01:39.800
♪ La-da-da-da,
la-da-da ♪

01:44.805 --> 01:46.574
Lumpy Space Princess,

01:46.607 --> 01:49.276
you were buried in candy and it
didn't change you at all.

01:49.310 --> 01:51.646
Why doesn't this elemental
stuff affect you?

01:51.679 --> 01:53.514
I'm a tough tranch!

01:53.548 --> 01:54.849
People don't tell me what to do,

01:54.882 --> 01:56.417
I tell them what to do!

01:56.451 --> 01:59.487
Okay, but it has to be
more than that.

01:59.520 --> 02:02.590
Like, you're not from around
Ooo, not really.

02:02.623 --> 02:05.426
Maybe you're not made of
the same stuff as us.

02:05.460 --> 02:07.595
Hmm.

02:07.628 --> 02:12.633
Lumps! Lumps are the subspace
molecular lattice

02:12.667 --> 02:15.202
that binds together
the scientific and magical

02:15.235 --> 02:18.305
forces of Ooo --
more powerful than

02:18.339 --> 02:20.508
any one element,
it's the force that

02:20.541 --> 02:23.310
orders reality into
its true shape.

02:23.344 --> 02:26.647
And, LSP, this part is very,
very important --

02:26.681 --> 02:28.148
Grrr!
No more learning!

02:33.421 --> 02:35.155
[ Car horn beeps ]

02:35.189 --> 02:40.060
Hey, Michael!
Let's get married.

02:42.530 --> 02:44.331
Wait, what?

02:44.365 --> 02:46.734
Michael.

02:46.767 --> 02:48.536
LSP, This is important.

02:48.569 --> 02:50.237
I think they were trying
to tell you --

02:50.270 --> 02:52.206
you're the anti-elemental.

02:52.239 --> 02:54.675
Fire, Ice, Candy, Slime and...

02:54.709 --> 02:57.177
Lumps!
[ Gasps ]

02:57.211 --> 02:59.914
[ Hums ]

03:04.385 --> 03:05.853
Huh?

03:05.886 --> 03:08.022
I must have dozed off...

03:08.055 --> 03:10.391
and bound myself.

03:12.226 --> 03:13.694
Ouch!

03:13.728 --> 03:15.362
[ Clears throat ]

03:15.396 --> 03:18.833
People say you shouldn't
live in the past!

03:18.866 --> 03:21.736
But I say, "Why not?"

03:21.769 --> 03:23.604
I love it.

03:23.638 --> 03:24.772
This book is strange,

03:24.805 --> 03:26.373
but when you puzzle it out,

03:26.407 --> 03:28.208
it's mostly all charges
and frequencies.

03:28.242 --> 03:30.044
Instead of fixing Ooo,

03:30.077 --> 03:32.112
I can use these jewels
to make a portal

03:32.146 --> 03:34.114
to take me back in time
and find Simon

03:34.148 --> 03:36.016
before he discovers
the crown.

03:36.050 --> 03:37.452
Uh-huh.

03:37.485 --> 03:39.386
This time I won't
let him put it on.

03:39.420 --> 03:41.522
I'll drop it in a volcano
before that happens.

03:41.556 --> 03:44.191
Things will be back to being
just me and Simon,

03:44.224 --> 03:46.527
and you won't exist!

03:46.561 --> 03:48.128
Mm-hm, mm-hm.

03:48.162 --> 03:50.465
No more Ice King,
no more magic Betty --

03:50.498 --> 03:53.568
maybe I can even stop
the Mushroom War!

03:53.601 --> 03:56.804
[ Laughs ]

03:56.837 --> 03:59.574
Cool.
Now where do I come in?

03:59.607 --> 04:01.075
You're not listening.

04:01.108 --> 04:03.911
My wonderful Simon will never
become this sad,

04:03.944 --> 04:05.880
pathetic creature
strewn before me.

04:05.913 --> 04:07.247
Wait, what?

04:07.281 --> 04:09.550
I thought I could do it,
but I can't.

04:09.584 --> 04:12.252
Being with you is like looking
at my old life

04:12.286 --> 04:14.054
through a funhouse mirror.

04:14.088 --> 04:18.325
[ Laughs ]
It's driving me mad.

04:20.528 --> 04:22.497
Goodbye, Ice King.

04:22.530 --> 04:25.466
[ Machine whirs ]

04:25.500 --> 04:28.636
Okay, I think this is a pretty
good breakdown

04:28.669 --> 04:30.270
of your components.

04:30.304 --> 04:31.806
We just need to figure out a way

04:31.839 --> 04:34.775
to tap into your pure
anti-elemental essence, LSP.

04:34.809 --> 04:37.945
[ Sighs ] Don't tell me
what to do, Finn.

04:37.978 --> 04:39.146
Yeah, like that.

04:39.179 --> 04:41.281
Pb is undiluted sweetness now,

04:41.315 --> 04:43.851
and Slime Princess has never
been slimier.

04:43.884 --> 04:47.121
I think you might need to be the
most you that you've ever been.

04:47.154 --> 04:49.624
You just have to believe in
yourself.

04:49.657 --> 04:51.325
I do believe myself.

04:51.358 --> 04:53.861
I'm a blossoming debutante
on the war path.

04:53.894 --> 04:56.631
Wenk!

04:56.664 --> 04:58.132
Ahhhhh!

04:58.165 --> 04:59.466
Wenk!

04:59.500 --> 05:02.036
Wenk! Wenk-wenk! Wenk, wenk,
wenk, wenk.

05:02.069 --> 05:05.172
[ Purrs ]
See?

05:11.512 --> 05:13.848
It's working.

05:13.881 --> 05:15.616
Ugh!
You okay?

05:15.650 --> 05:18.318
Just relax, you'll be
obliterated soon.

05:18.352 --> 05:23.423
Really? Lady, this Simon sounds
cool, but I'm Ice King.

05:25.693 --> 05:29.329
I, uh, I guess
I'm a special person

05:29.363 --> 05:31.666
and I am worthy of respect.

05:31.699 --> 05:34.168
Just -- shh!
It'll be over in a second.

05:34.201 --> 05:37.404
Can you turn this off
and we can talk, maybe?

05:37.437 --> 05:39.574
Nertz.

05:45.512 --> 05:48.583
Huh.

05:48.616 --> 05:51.518
♪ Underneath the prairie

05:51.552 --> 05:53.554
♪ Over sugar springs

05:53.588 --> 05:56.190
♪ We'll sing our song forever

05:56.223 --> 05:59.026
♪ This candy chorus rings

05:59.059 --> 06:01.261
♪ La-da-da-da, la-da-da

06:01.295 --> 06:03.831
Boy, did I fail deep.

06:03.864 --> 06:06.867
Well, maybe I'll try again in
another 1,000 years.

06:06.901 --> 06:09.403
I'm not sticking around to see
how this ends.

06:09.436 --> 06:12.573
Mr. Fox, please roll me
someplace safe.

06:14.308 --> 06:17.511
Oh, oh, wow. Okay.

06:17.544 --> 06:19.513
[ Grunts ]

06:19.546 --> 06:21.448
♪ Overlook the valley

06:21.481 --> 06:23.283
♪ Under honeymoon

06:23.317 --> 06:26.120
What if?
Oh!

06:28.422 --> 06:30.725
We're running out of time.

06:30.758 --> 06:34.629
I am.
Glob!

06:34.662 --> 06:37.431
Ding-dong.

06:37.464 --> 06:39.734
It's me, classic Ice King!

06:39.767 --> 06:41.101
Si-men!

06:41.135 --> 06:42.402
I didn't like
being ditched earlier,

06:42.436 --> 06:43.938
but if you and Betty
are cool now,

06:43.971 --> 06:46.406
you can help us figure out how
to use LSP's power.

06:46.440 --> 06:48.442
Wait, where's Betty?

06:48.475 --> 06:51.445
Who?

06:51.478 --> 06:53.914
Here, I bet this thing
can help
you.

06:53.948 --> 06:58.953
[ Gasps ] It's Gunter!
Hey, Gunter! Come here, boy.

06:58.986 --> 07:01.656
Okay, fair.

07:01.689 --> 07:04.424
Hey, LSP, now that we've got
the Enchiridion,

07:04.458 --> 07:06.093
maybe we can study it for
a way to figu--

07:06.126 --> 07:07.962
No more studying!

07:07.995 --> 07:10.998
All day long you've been telling
me what to do.

07:11.031 --> 07:16.203
I already saved your life,
so quit telling me what to do.

07:19.273 --> 07:21.942
Huh?

07:21.976 --> 07:24.779
What's happening?

07:24.812 --> 07:26.681
The jewels.

07:26.714 --> 07:29.650
Oh!
What if your force of will

07:29.684 --> 07:34.421
is influencing and attracting
elemental magic.

07:34.454 --> 07:36.623
You mean these jewels love me

07:36.657 --> 07:38.826
more than they love those
dumb-dumbs?

07:38.859 --> 07:40.460
[ Laughs ]

07:40.494 --> 07:42.329
Wenk! Wenk! Wenk!
And you!

07:42.362 --> 07:44.832
Clam your face, you noid!

07:47.367 --> 07:49.937
Clam your face,
you noid!

07:49.970 --> 07:52.172
Okay.

07:57.678 --> 07:59.313
Wenk!

07:59.346 --> 08:01.816
My boy!

08:01.849 --> 08:05.052
You bossed him back to normal.
Don't stop.

08:05.085 --> 08:09.523
Uh, I don't think I can.
The jelly is out of the tube.

08:13.828 --> 08:16.630
♪ Underneath the mountain

08:16.663 --> 08:18.665
♪ Overlook the sea

08:18.699 --> 08:20.835
♪ I find my sweet friends
waiting ♪

08:20.868 --> 08:23.070
♪ And bring them close to me

08:23.103 --> 08:25.505
Mama, Papa!

08:25.539 --> 08:28.876
♪ Close to me

08:28.909 --> 08:30.911
Excuse me.

08:33.213 --> 08:34.882
Whoop!

08:40.420 --> 08:43.223
Oh, blessings, what a trip.

08:43.257 --> 08:45.159
Hey, Slime Princess.

08:45.192 --> 08:47.361
Oh! Hello, Jake.

08:47.394 --> 08:50.030
Uh, did you recently get
a haircut?

08:50.064 --> 08:54.869
Unnnh. Lumps.

08:54.902 --> 08:57.037
Oh, LSP.

08:57.071 --> 09:00.274
Please be careful with yourself.

09:10.417 --> 09:13.220
Ha-ha, fine, I guess.

09:13.253 --> 09:15.255
Yeah, that's all of them!

09:15.289 --> 09:17.758
[ Groans ]

09:20.828 --> 09:23.630
LSP!

09:23.663 --> 09:27.401
[ Weakly ]
I'm a hero.

09:32.339 --> 09:35.275
Whoops.

09:35.309 --> 09:36.977
You did it.

09:37.011 --> 09:38.712
She did it!

09:38.745 --> 09:40.614
[ Cheers and applause ]

09:40.647 --> 09:43.483
Uh, I'd like to date you, LSP.

09:43.517 --> 09:46.486
Thank you, Starchy.

09:46.520 --> 09:51.091
[ Coughing ]

09:51.125 --> 09:54.394
Wait, where --
Up here.

09:54.428 --> 09:58.365
[ Clicks tongue ]
You really donked up.

09:59.967 --> 10:02.236
Finn?
Jake?

10:02.269 --> 10:05.439
Finn!

10:05.472 --> 10:09.109
Oh, my gosh!

10:09.143 --> 10:11.111
Come here.

10:11.145 --> 10:12.913
What?
Over here.

10:12.947 --> 10:16.350
Hey, buddy.

10:16.383 --> 10:19.286
Jake? Are you okay?

10:19.319 --> 10:20.787
Yeah...
[ Chuckles ]

10:20.821 --> 10:23.457
You know, everything looks
different after a long trip.

10:23.490 --> 10:28.795
You and I can fix whatever this
is together, whenever.

10:28.829 --> 10:30.297
Fix what now?

10:30.330 --> 10:33.300
I was really scared
when you left.

10:33.333 --> 10:35.502
You're my best brother.

10:37.972 --> 10:39.739
I love you.

10:42.742 --> 10:46.613
♪ Come along with me

10:46.646 --> 10:51.018
♪ And the butterflies and bees

10:53.653 --> 10:56.556
This is party is so crazy!
